Class SnappingBehavior

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
IActivatable, IAdaptable.Bound<IVisualPart<? extends javafx.scene.Node>>, IBehavior
public class SnappingBehavior extends AbstractBehavior
The SnappingBehavior is responsible for creating and removing feedback and handles in response to SnappingModel changes.
